spec_data.Name: perl-LWP-UserAgent-DNS-Hosts
spec_data.Description:
LWP::UserAgent::DNS::Hosts is a module to override HTTP/HTTPS request peer
addresses that uses LWP::UserAgent.  This module concept was got from
LWP::Protocol::PSGI.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:42:33 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Override LWP HTTP/HTTPS request's host like /etc/hosts
